00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:54,400
must have the courage to make decisions

5
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,630
and have a clean record.

6
00:00:56,630 --> 00:01:00,710
[ From Talmud ]
Judge Han Soo Ho, are you that kind of person?

7
00:01:07,630 --> 00:01:09,800
