11
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:25,990
Every hour you're not in love is a waste of time.

12
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:27,970
That? Well...

13
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:30,620
Kang Ho.

14
00:01:30,670 --> 00:01:34,670
Do you know why being in jail is a waste of time?

15
00:01:34,670 --> 00:01:36,470
Because you can't make money?

16
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:38,670
